@startuml US12-SSD
autonumber

actor "Product Owner" as PO
participant "System" as S

PO -> S: Access cargo generation simulator
S --> PO: Display simulator configuration options

PO -> S: Configure simulation parameters (optional)
S --> PO: Display updated configuration

PO -> S: Start cargo simulation
S --> PO: Confirm simulation started

PO -> S: Request cargo generation status
S --> PO: Display current cargo generation statistics

PO -> S: View generated cargoes
S --> PO: Display list of generated cargoes

PO -> S: Adjust simulation parameters (optional)
S --> PO: Confirm parameter adjustments

PO -> S: Pause/stop simulation (optional)
S --> PO: Confirm simulation status change

@enduml